Description: Our facility for independent Seniors 62+. We offer one and two bedroom apartment homes feature fully equipped kitchens, wall to wall carpeting, central heat and air conditioning. Comfort features include grab bars in the bathrooms and conveniently located emergency pull cords. This four story elevator building has three wings which wrap around a beautifully landscaped courtyard with fountain. We offer planned activities in the Community Room. Residents also have access to a Wellness Center, a Computer Room, Exercise area and Craft Room. Conveniently located on Mike Shapiro Drive, minutes from neighborhood shopping including grocery stores and pharmacies. Southern Maryland Hospital, places of worship, a library and parks are also close by. We ensure a high level of commitment to treating residents with compassion and patience.
